reviewText: We had this when my daughter was younger in VHS form. I wanted to share it with my new husband. So I got the DVD form.
I love this movie,it was a favorite movie of mine as a child and I love to be able to get on Amazon and find all my older movies .
Great movie and arrived very quickly
I already had this movie on VHS and wanted the DVD.
Excellent movie! THis is a really good one to watch if you have a small child, great family film!

This is a fun video, with a touching performance by Depardieu. He shows a gentle side as he helps a small boy face his mother's sudden death. Depardieu and Goldberg dance together at one point which is particularly delightful! Good for all ages!
